今日<br />\n<blockquote>立法會換屆選舉規模極大：440萬名登記選民、70個議席、615個投票站、<span class=\"red\">34 000名選舉工作人員</span></blockquote><br />\n<blockquote><em>777：香港選舉有一點比較獨特，就是我們有一個中央點票站，即是將屬功能組別的區議會（第二）的選票，集齊以點票。據我所知，<span class=\"red\">中央點票站的點票人員可能有一萬人</span></em></blockquote>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T17:01:07.000Z","msg":"兩個月後請多三千人、亞博多成五千人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n国安嚟？"},{"pid":"d7a87b6a4bf437703368b3e9f97e1b9aa9fd53cb","tid":2134351,"uid":4850,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T17:03:38.000Z","msg":"啲廢老好快死哂啦，老人院群組，睇下出年點投<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc19f286e07d9bef4524bfb99e485f2e3484f1f6","tid":2134351,"uid":215113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T17:05:36.000Z","msg":"長者根本唔撚應該比佢地投<br />\n一黎個個都冇哂思考<br />\n二黎佢地都就死 邊個選到基本上都唔關佢地事"},{"pid":"93418794aa5de73d8c793b073978076e614e33c8","tid":2134351,"uid":359683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T17:10:50.000Z","msg":"投票從來都有成本架啦<br />\n台灣人為左投票比自己支持嘅候選人<br />\n坐飛機都要返去投票<br />\n<br />\n年輕人一樣可以怕疫情而唔出黎投票<br />\n扮哂關顧老人家根本全部都係廢話"},{"pid":"f9d47b26845e39ee8e97d3018bb38e828945c57d","tid":2134351,"uid":1977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T18:57:53.000Z","msg":"放棄係人地權利"},{"pid":"47e82d7bde440e888a68a3373466f6b60ae3a49a","tid":2134351,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d7a87b6a4bf437703368b3e9f97e1b9aa9fd53cb","tid":2134351,"uid":4850,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T17:03:38.000Z","msg":"啲廢老好快死哂啦，老人院群組，睇下出年點投<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />